<strong style="color: #F59E0B;">ROLE:</strong> [Who you want it to be]<br>
<strong style="color: #F59E0B;">TASK:</strong> [What you want done]<br>
<strong style="color: #F59E0B;">FORMAT:</strong> [How you want it output]<br>
<strong style="color: #F59E0B;">CONSTRAINTS:</strong> [What to avoid]
</p>
</div>

<p style="color: #A1A1AA; margin-bottom: 2rem;">That's it. Four lines. No fancy formatting. No "act as a world-class expert."</p>

<h2 style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;">Examples</h2>

